snippet.title: Mullet Hell Trailer
snippet.description: Introducing the hairiest survival game you've every played! Blast your way through hair curling enemies to prove you are worthy of the mullet! Mullet Hell is a casual rogue-like, reverse bullet hell where you must fend off foes who seek to remove your luscious locks from your head.
